# Beautiful Soup
Easy do learn
No JavaScript support
Inefficient

# Selenium (SE)
Is a webdriver designed to render web pages for test automation of web applications.
Works with JavaScript.
Easy to learn than Scrapy.
Slower than http requests because all the JS in the page will be executed.
God option if speed is not a problem.

# Scraping
Scraping is a web scraping framework built specially for web scraping and written entirely in Python.
Most complete web scraping tool in Python.
Is harder to learn.
It is asynchronous and fast.
You can store data in database.
Create crawlers.